            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="34181140">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">原文“During the nineteenth century, the formation of marriage ties, for most groups in the population, became based on considerations other than judgements of economic value”

此处“在19世纪期间，婚姻纽带的形式就大部分群体而言是以经济价值的判断和考虑为基础的”疑为讹误。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-02-01 08:57</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
